measurements.description: Approximately 882 flowers and 352 buds on 73 nicely arranged up-to 28-cm infloresences, ten of those juvenile; symmetrical plant 70cm wide by 30cm tall above pot, grown in 30-cm plastic bulb pot, bark media; sepals and petals sparkling white, red markings basally; lip saccate, white, orange markings;; substance firm; texture crystalline; also award #20235379.
